# Keep only KB-scale jsonl + summaries in git; ignore bulky serve/eval logs,
# token dumps, venvs, and the temporary pinned serve copy (wirbel #682 convention,
# PR #690 disk constraint — shared overlay is tight).
_serve_*/
_pinproof_*/
_logs/
*.serve.log
*.out
*.pid
__pycache__/
decode_outputs*.jsonl
*.eval
